Package: oanda
Title: R implementation of OANDA V2 API
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Lawrence",
           family = "Khan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "LK1186@NYU.EDU")
Description: A set of robust R functions that implements OANDA's V2 HTTP API for algorithmic trading. The package creation was motivated by the need to quickly move research into executable trades in a production system. With this package one can access account information, place, modify, cancel an order. 
